    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/4d918a959f87ccb0570d79eb6faea4d9.avif?t=1761719837\" width=620 height=80 /></span><br><br><strong>感谢大家关注《命运英雄》，获取最新游戏讯息。<br>可以加入官方QQ社群①（已满）：663542787 <br>QQ社群②：837334501 <br>联系我们！<br> 点击加入QQ讨论①群 <br> 点击加入QQ讨论②群 </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/13c4eccdbcf6f90b4451eae5fdf3eec1.avif?t=1761719837\" width=620 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/dd5ebf521b15fe4b189ca4d644a815ae.poster.avif?t=1761719837\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/dd5ebf521b15fe4b189ca4d644a815ae.webm?t=1761719837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/dd5ebf521b15fe4b189ca4d644a815ae.mp4?t=1761719837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>《命运英雄》是一款以“幸存者”为核心玩法的爽快割草类“肉鸽”游戏，我们在传统“幸存者”独自游玩的基础上，添加了可陪伴主角共同出战的多职业伙伴和守护灵系统。<br>每场战斗最多可携带4个队友和1个守护灵，让大家可以在游戏中可以体验到5倍的畅爽割草乐趣！<br>同时，你还可以扮演不同角色，体会超多不同的职业技能，组建属于你自己的独特伙伴队伍，在重重怪物群的包围之下生存下去，亦可以通过命运探索，战胜强力BOSS，获得多种随机守护灵与你共同并肩作战，最终击败超级大魔王！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/0b962aa4a6b3b1eb1a72881a9a2b2ed8.avif?t=1761719837\" width=620 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/1b3545a40b64938d86661969a0d50fad.poster.avif?t=1761719837\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/1b3545a40b64938d86661969a0d50fad.webm?t=1761719837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/1b3545a40b64938d86661969a0d50fad.mp4?t=1761719837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>自由选择游戏出战角色，体验8大特色技能派系元素（雷、风、冰、火、土、毒、圣、暗），自由搭配组合N种不同的攻击技能，每种搭配都有不同的战技效果，每个角色每次进入游戏都是全新的体验，丰富的Rogue元素，爽就完事了。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/7ab9c45b9809c9f7f2ee751b3e2d9c90.avif?t=1761719837\" width=620 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/f78102cce5323cc097ded76c0bfd9fda.poster.avif?t=1761719837\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/f78102cce5323cc097ded76c0bfd9fda.webm?t=1761719837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/f78102cce5323cc097ded76c0bfd9fda.mp4?t=1761719837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>游戏内有超过多种风格迥异，技能效果各异守护灵，等着你来发现！<br>它们可以陪你一起战斗，给你叠加buff，给你更多功能性的玩法选择<br>总之，守护灵非常强！强到离谱！能打！能抗！还能辅助！<br>而守护灵外观也各式各样，丰富多彩，比如：“来自地狱的伯爵，骨罗姆”！</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/d0236697b901ec5a660e2a41e900082d.avif?t=1761719837\" width=620 height=80 /></span><br><br><strong>谁说Roguelite 玩法就只有刷刷刷？游戏中随机的命运玩法，让游戏内隐藏超多你意向不到的特殊惊喜。</strong><br><strong>比如：</strong><br><br><strong>酒馆可招募不同职业的队友，增强实力</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/b21260e67b16b57b98052e14a44373e6.poster.avif?t=1761719837\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/b21260e67b16b57b98052e14a44373e6.webm?t=1761719837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/b21260e67b16b57b98052e14a44373e6.mp4?t=1761719837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>遇到狡猾抢劫犯，是乖乖给钱？还是直接开干？</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/37249e39a70a81a23e6882ef51c53479.poster.avif?t=1761719837\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/37249e39a70a81a23e6882ef51c53479.webm?t=1761719837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332410/extras/37249e39a70a81a23e6882ef51c53479.mp4?t=1761719837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏中随机的命运玩法，让游戏内隐藏超多你意向不到的特殊惊喜。<br><br>每一次的选择都是一次全新的体验；<br><br>每一次选择都代表着不同的结局；<br><br>每一次选择都会让你感受到命运的抉择！<br><br>或生，或死，或悲，或乐，一切都由你亲手开启！",
